1.value:
Staffing


The intention is to implement the direct sales process in a structured fashion - and the ramp  up of staff will reflect that.

The first to be employed will be a CTO and developer to free up Gordon Guthrie to switch to full time sales and marketing.

An end-to-end online process (supported by the existing built-in metrics and funnel measurement system) will then be implemented.

The performance of this process will then be managed (lower cost, higher conversion, better yield) - with additional staff being taken on as it develops.

Management/Executive costs will grow slowly as well.
